Particules/Sprites emitter factory plugin with jQuery & CSS3 V0.4
by molokoloco@gmail.com 23/10/2011 - MIT/GPL

  * Infos : http://www.b2bweb.fr/emitter-sprites-particules-factory-with-jquery-css3
  * Sources : https://github.com/molokoloco/jquery.emitter
  * Plain demo : http://www.b2bweb.fr/framework/jquery.emitter/jquery.emitter.html

